---
layout: layouts/base
title: "Bingsjöstämmans {{ year }}"
year: 2024
eleventyComputed:
  permalink: "{% if year == editions.current %}/index.html{% else %}/{{ year }}/index.html{% endif %}"
  isArchive: "{{ year != editions.current }}"
---

<h1>Bingsjöstämmans {{ year }}</h1>
<p>Välkommen till festivalen!</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="{% if year == editions.current %}/lineup/{% else %}/{{ year }}/lineup/{% endif %}">Artister {{ year }}</a></li>
</ul>

{% if isArchive %}
<div class="archive-banner">
  This is an archive from {{ year }}.
  <a href="/">View current festival →</a>
</div>
<meta name="robots" content="noindex">
{% endif %}

{% if isArchive == "true" %}
  <p class="ticket-info">
    Detta är en arkiverad utgåva. Aktuella biljettpriser visas inte.
  </p>
{% else %}
  <p class="ticket-info">
    <strong>Biljettpriser {{ year }}:</strong><br>
    {% price "Vuxen", "general" %}
    {% price "Ungdom", "youth" %}
    {% price "Camping", "camping" %}
  </p>
{% endif %}

